name: Apple iPad Air 5th Gen
description: The latest Apple iPad Air 5th Gen features an all-screen design with stunning Blue color. It has a 10.9-inch (2360x1640) LED‑backlit Multi‑Touch Liquid Retina display. The 10.9-inch Liquid Retina display features advanced technologies like True Tone, P3 wide color, and an anti‑reflective coating. It offers a 2360x1640‑pixel resolution at 264 pixels per inch (PPI). Apple Touch ID is built into the top button, so you can use your fingerprint to unlock your iPad and sign in to apps.

name: Xiaomi Mi Smart Projector 2
description: The Xiaomi Mi Smart Projector 2 is a compact projector from Xiaomi. It offers excellent image quality with FHD 1080p resolution, multi-angle keystone correction, and the inclusion of Android TV. It delivers high-quality images and sharp details. It comes with a brightness of up to 500 ANSI lumens and the use of diffuse reflection. The Mi Smart Projector 2 features automatic multi-angle keystone correction across 3 axes and 6 directions to provide a perfect rectangle, so you don't have to spend long minutes manually correcting it. The Smart Projector 2 comes equipped with a 3.5mm audio jack, a USB 2.0 port and an HDMI 2.0 port, the latter with 4K video input.

Its 24.1MP photos and 4K movies are clear, sharp, and packed with colour even in low light. This is thanks to an APS-C sensor, powerful autofocus and DIGIC 8 with Digital Lens Optimizer. The Vari-Angle touchscreen makes awkward angles and selfies easy.
